What you need to know:

With races cancelled globally, Boston Marathon Champion Cherono is among runners struggling to meet the cost of medication and to fend for their families.  With the help of his manager, he has paid for part of his daughter’s medication but his mother’s cancer treatment has put additional burden on the familyWeighed down by medical bills, athlete and his family is forced to disrupt his training schedule to take care of his ailing child until his management team comes to his rescue